OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1775916666
OL,3,CMan in his seventies hospitalised in a
OL,4,Ccritical condition after alleged
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,FA man in his seventies is in a
OL,8,Fcritical condition after an alleged
OL,9,Fassault in Cheltenham.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to a
OL,12,Freport of an assault on Honeybourne
OL,13,FWay near Waitrose at around 7.30pm on
OL,14,FWednesday 8 April. The victim was
OL,15,Ftaken to Gloucestershire Royal
OL,16,FHospital where he remains in a
OL,17,Fcritical condition.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
