PN,43502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1775916666
OL,3,CMan in his seventies hospitalised in a
OL,4,Ccritical condition after alleged
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,FPolice in Gloucestershire have
OL,8,Freleased CCTV images of two men they
OL,9,Fwould like to identify in connection
OL,10,Fwith the incident.
OL,12,FShortly before the incident took
OL,13,Fplace, it was reported that the two
OL,14,Fmen had been on the Millennium Bridge
OL,15,Fand had thrown a large branch at a
OL,16,Fcyclist who was travelling on the road
OL,17,Fbelow. It is not believed the cyclist
OL,18,Fwas injured.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1775916666
OL,3,CMan in his seventies hospitalised in a
OL,4,Ccritical condition after alleged
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,FThe men then left the bridge and were
OL,8,Fapproached by the victim on
OL,9,FHoneybourne Way. It is reported an
OL,10,Fexchange took place between them
OL,11,Fbefore one of the men punched the
OL,12,Fvictim in the face causing him to fall
OL,13,Fto the ground.
OL,15,FThe two men then fled before officers
OL,16,Farrived at the scene. Closures are
OL,17,Fcurrently in place while a forensic
OL,18,Fexaminations take place.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1775916666
OL,3,CMan in his seventies hospitalised in a
OL,4,Ccritical condition after alleged
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,FThey are expected to remain in place
OL,8,Ffor some time and members of the
OL,9,Fpublic are asked to plan alternative
OL,10,Froutes while officers conduct their
OL,11,Finvestigation.
OL,13,FGloucestershire Constabulary said:
OL,14,F"One of the men is described as being
OL,15,Fwhite, aged between 20 and 30, of a
OL,16,Fmuscular build and bald. He was
OL,17,Fwearing a black T-shirt with white
OL,18,Fwriting across the front, black
OL,19,Fshorts, black socks and grey shoes.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1775916666
OL,3,CMan in his seventies hospitalised in a
OL,4,Ccritical condition after alleged
OL,5,Cassault
OL,7,F"The second man is also described as
OL,8,Fbeing white and of a similar age. He
OL,9,Fwas topless and was wearing black
OL,10,Fshorts with a logo on the bottom of
OL,11,Fthe left leg, a grey cap, white socks
OL,12,Fand grey trainers."
OL,14,FAnyone who recognises the men, has any
OL,15,Finformation or relevant footage, is
OL,16,Fasked to contact the police.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
